Dispute Resolution
- **Between Users and Experts/Professionals**:   - Parties are encouraged to resolve disputes amicably through direct communication.   - If unresolved, disputes can be escalated to The Expert AI's support team for mediation. - **Legal Jurisdiction**:   - Any unresolved disputes will be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts in as decided by The Expert AI.
Refund Policy
